DISCIPLINARY CASES

2014-0997. Columbus Bar Assn. v. Armengau.

On motion for interim remedial suspension. Javier Horacio Armengau, Attorney Registration No. 0069776, is suspended from the practice of law for an interim period. Relator shall appoint an attorney to inventory respondent’s files.

O’Neill, J., dissents as to the imposition of the suspension.
